04/The-Weeknd-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/The-Weeknd-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/The-Weeknd-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/The-Weeknd-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/The-Weeknd">The Weeknd</a>承诺从他的 XO 人道主义基金中拨款 200 万美元（160 万英镑）来帮助饱受战争蹂躏的加沙家庭提供食物。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-dawn-fm-review-3132463">《The Weeknd》——“黎明 FM”评论：深情的明星带着希望和后见之明迎接新的一天</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位歌手的真名是 Abel Tesfaye，XO 人道主义基金帮助对抗全球饥饿。据<a href="https://www.wfp.org/news/world-food-programme-goodwill-ambassador-weeknd-help-provide-18-million-loaves-bread-families" target="_blank" rel="noopener">世界粮食计划署 ​​(WFP)</a>称，这笔捐款将提供超过 1,500 吨强化小麦面粉，这些面粉将用于制作约 1800 万条面包，可以帮助超过 157,000 名巴勒斯坦人一个月的食物。</p><p>特斯法耶是联合国世界粮食计划署亲善大使， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-sends-2-5million-to-gaza-for-emergency-meals-3552225">此前曾于 2023 年底捐赠 250 万美元（190 万英镑），</a>提供 820 吨食品包，为超过 173,000 名巴勒斯坦人提供两周的食物。</p><p>他还呼吁粉丝们为世界粮食计划署的人道主义努力捐款。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5q6NWopt83/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;